comments.body:
@rhatdan Sorry, missed the bot action on this. I commented in the issue thread when it got marked stale (https://github.com/containers/podman/issues/8432#issuecomment-801533225) but not here.

I wasn't able to get `make validate`, `make lint`, and tests to run locally when I was working on it; the last of those stopped me from creating a validation/regression test to pass the CI checks (and I think it does deserve a test). I still plan to revisit, but it's been a very busy month.


Beyond general review of my approach, the only open code question on my end was whether `FinishedAt` should retain its old value after restore (matching docker) or reset to nil once the container is running (what I did, not realizing it was _not_ what docker did until the very end).
